headline: Autodesk (ADSK) Valuation: Is There More Upside After Recent Share Price Consolidation?
summary: Autodesk (ADSK) shares have seen moderate movements in recent weeks, as investors weigh the company’s performance and longer-term growth in the context of its latest financial results. Recent trading suggests a period of consolidation for the stock. See our latest analysis for Autodesk. Autodesk’s share price has been steady this year, holding close to $299 after a modest 2% gain year-to-date.
